@@ -0,0 +1,23 @@
+# LoongArch64 Bzlmod Smoke Workspace
+
+Run this workspace from inside a patched `rules_rust` checkout:
+
+```bash
+cd loongarch64_adaptation/smoke_bzlmod
+bazel sync
+bazel test //:smoke_test
+bazel run //:smoke_bin
+```
+
+Expected `bazel run` output:
+
+```text
+loongarch64-smoke:64
+```
+
+This validates:
+- Bzlmod local override of the patched `rules_rust`;
+- Rust 1.77.2 LoongArch64 host toolchain download and registration;
+- `rust_library`, `rust_test`, and `rust_binary`;
+- `cargo_build_script` execution and `cargo:rustc-env` propagation;
+- `crate_universe` `from_specs` for a third-party crate on `loongarch64-unknown-linux-gnu`.
